channel.title: Comments on: 9 Plyometric Exercises For Explosive Tennis
channel.description: Your secret weapon on the court.

item.title: By: Adrian
item.dc:creator: Adrian
item.description: How’s it going? Great exercises which I’ve started incorporating into my workouts. I started the medicine ball throws and did 10 reps each variation, soon afterwards my left side of my back started aching, this was Thursday it’s now Saturday and it doesn’t feel like normal lower back pain, feels more internal. Is there a chance my core got overworked or twisted or something?
